sentences.english: This is the starting value for the two data sets.
sentences.chinese: 这是两个数据集的起始值。

sentences.english: Uncover the starting and ending points and start filling in the blanks one at a time.
sentences.chinese: 找到起始点，然后开始填补空白。

sentences.english: The server part of the channel is located at the start of the server context sink chain.
sentences.chinese: 通道的伺服器部分位在伺服器内容接收链结的起始端。

sentences.english: Write the words in front of, summing up the work starting.
sentences.chinese: 即写在前面的话，工作总结起始的段落。

sentences.english: Gets the starting column of a script block in the generated source file.
sentences.chinese: 获取生成资源文件中某个脚本块的起始列。

sentences.english: You create a new project that deals with requirements for a new starship generation.
sentences.chinese: 您需要为一个新的起始代，创建一个新项目。

sentences.english: Take a look at the start page for an example of the inclusion.
sentences.chinese: 在起始页中可看到包含的示例。

sentences.english: The appointment form must have a start date field.
sentences.chinese: 约会表单必须有一个起始日期字段。

sentences.english: He stood there at the starting line with a regular piece of paper.
sentences.chinese: 他那这一张普通的纸站在起始线上。

sentences.english: A melancholy fold, which resembled the beginning of irony, wrinkled her right cheek.
sentences.chinese: 一条含愁的皱痕横在她的右脸上，仿佛是冷笑的起始。

sentences.english: Attributes are always added to the start tag of an HTML element.
sentences.chinese: 属性应该添加在HTML元素里的起始标签中。

sentences.english: There is a hypermethylation sequential basis in the upstream region from the transcriptional start site of IRX1 gene.
sentences.chinese: IRX1基因转录起始点上游存在高甲基化结构基础。

sentences.english: This is regarded as the beginning of barehanded martial arts and healthcare martial arts.
sentences.chinese: 以上是徒手武术而后保健武术的起始。

sentences.english: Ancona now starts as a rebel region.
sentences.chinese: 安科纳现在起始是叛乱地区。

sentences.english: “For us the starting point is always the science,” Dr. McGill said.
sentences.chinese: “对我们来说，科学就是起始点，”麦克吉尔博士说。

sentences.english: Designates the start or destination of a hypertext link.
sentences.chinese: 表示超链接的起始或目的位置。
